window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A spicy paranormal romance novella</p> <p>Harper is a witch.</p> <p>The protégé in the Night Garden coven to her mother’s position, she wanted to forge her own path, taking jobs from the more questionable types to frame the even less favorable type.</p> <p>Benjamin is a merman.</p> <p>Opening his shop, Seven Seas Aquariums &amp; Sealife, he lived a relatively quiet life. Growing coral, herbs and plant life and teaching people about the creatures in the sea brought him peace.</p> <p>When Benjamin has a target painted on his back, one that Harper is aimed for, he unsuspectingly lets her into his life. Only, Harper can’t find what she needs to finish the job. And her client is getting suspicious.</p> <p>Welcome to Pharos Hills.</p> <p>A picturesque, little town on the Virginian east coast.</p> <p>We invite you to share in all the beauty it has to offer.</p> <p>And all the not so beautiful.</p> <p>Because, after all…</p> <p>When you live amongst monsters, you’re bound to find ardent desire.</p>"; 
